{"lastModified":1761320254162,"uri":"c::16875063630::vessel::d5cc79e9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sydney, Australia\n\nFollowing an extensive refit in June 2023, SHADOW emerges as the newest and most impressive superyacht on Sydney Harbour.\n\nAs a 100-foot luxury cruiser, SHADOW provides a seamless blend of comfort and sophistication. It is an ideal choice for intimate events, accommodating two people, as well as private parties or corporate gatherings of up to 90 guests. The yacht features beautifully designed upper and lower deck cabins, spacious front and rear decks, and four bedrooms, each with its own ensuite bathroom. The refurbishment has included all-new custom seating on the bow, allowing guests to enjoy an unparalleled view as they pass beneath the iconic Sydney Harbour Bridge.\n\nExploring Sydney Harbour on SHADOW allows you to experience the city’s iconic landmarks from a whole new perspective. Glide along the pristine waters and marvel at the Sydney Opera House, the Sydney Harbour Bridge, and other defining features of this vibrant metropolis.\n\nWhether you’re planning a special occasion, entertaining corporate guests, or simply seeking a memorable outing, SHADOW’s Private Charters package promises an unparalleled experience. With its refined amenities, stylish design, and prime location, SHADOW invites you to indulge in the splendors of Sydney Harbour while creating lasting memories.","blueprint":{"name":"SHADOW","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc79e9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::20091620-50af-11ef-9c98-d7b983c29df7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc79e9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::860750e0-50af-11ef-9c98-d7b983c29df7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc79e9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::86083b40-50af-11ef-9c98-d7b983c29df7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc79e9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::a